{"tid":447744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社走訪自稱美國共產黨員：中共有如燈塔","createTime":"2017-10-25T14:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T15:24:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b84f8c35d4f8da7a0c23d0d4db181ca264941f0","tid":447744,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171025/s00004/4487cceae49b64c086ca425c986d02ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171025%2Fs00004%2F4487cceae49b64c086ca425c986d02ce.jpg&h=39416a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共十九大昨日閉幕，國家領導人習近平帶領新常委亮相，黨章的修訂亦意味着，中國要邁向新時代中國特色社會主義思想的方向發展。新華社在英國、澳洲、意大利、美國及泰國採訪，問及對於共產黨的看法和認識。<br />\n<br />\n綜合整段影片的訪問，受訪者認為中國共產黨員有堅定的信仰和優秀的品德，另有一自稱美國共產黨員的青年，讚揚中國共產黨員堅定信仰共產主義、馬克思主義，全心全意為人民服務。<br />\n<br />\n對於習近平，受訪者讚揚他是很有魅力很自信的領袖，又指他受人敬重，有執政理念和創意，帶領所有人前行。更有外國受訪者指出，有些歐洲人希望自己國家領袖像習近平一樣。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國共產黨，有受訪者表示印象很好，他又表示每個國家的民主進程和政制進程都不一樣，西方人應予以理解。又有美國共產黨員指，中國共產黨有如燈塔，世界各地的共產黨應該仿效。有泰國受訪者表示，沒有共產黨，中國不可能獲得巨大的進步。"},{"pid":"c5cf31a8e3f36620125ecdca8aa5ab415d42e876","tid":447744,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171025/s00004/1508937017416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171025%2Fs00004%2F1508937017416&d=ZXQQO6Nfw4eyMHcwSLxa0Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=727634c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171025%2Fs00004%2F1508937017416&h=2465ad7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171025/s00004/1508937017416</a>"},{"pid":"dcc1055f41308066cc1a4760fbcda3bfa63550a4","tid":447744,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共產有信仰"},{"pid":"334e525cbe39f70d5856cdf78c21fea7ece5ba45","tid":447744,"uid":37584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"唔係好明 點解成日恃住人多黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150087dfd38431cb8603fd0a3821e3ecb24a1beb","tid":447744,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"咁事實而家全地球的共產黨，最出位撈得最掂就係中共。"},{"pid":"adde06052e32d27ed1e7332ee0884532e6023f98","tid":447744,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"我又幾欣賞班友，比起留係西方國家拿住杯Starbucks話自己係共產主義者個班不明生物，最起碼做到言行一致"},{"pid":"3eba352e5de5dd9a96d1faeb79c24ab4c1c29b22","tid":447744,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[突發2032]五毛曼徹斯特聯被bam</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/447627/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/447627/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"f7a2f84b87c4507a3fb6b32cf0720279b7b4139c","tid":447744,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又幾欣賞班友，比起留係西方國家拿住杯Starbucks話自己係共產主義者個班不明生物，最起碼做到言行一致</blockquote><br />\n呢班係咪傳說中既托派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1308c0b74abe910a3b663b6cf5cb0ab4d5474e1","tid":447744,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"燈"}]}